Keeping this condition in mind, let us study the geometric picture of
the condensation of the tachyonic fluctuation. The locations of the
D-strings are specified by the eigenvalues of the Higgs field . 
We diagonalize the whole Higgs field including the fluctuation
(), as(The gauge fields are not diagonalized
